Please file this bug report at https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/new.

## What happened

I have no idea what happened but i am filling this bug as it is asked in the error i have got :) 
It didn't prevent me from using the plugin or the IDE, or anything.

## Version information

Android Studio `Arctic Fox | 2020.3.1` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 59.0.2` • Dart plugin `203.8292`

Error getting Flutter sdk information.
